net.dean.jraw.auth

Class ApatheticTokenStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.auth.ApatheticTokenStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TokenStore

    public final class ApatheticTokenStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements TokenStore
    A TokenStore implementation that disregards all calls to writeToken(String, String), returns false for all calls to isStored(String), and throws a NoSuchTokenException for all calls to readToken(String). Useful when using a RefreshTokenHandler which does not need to store any refresh tokens.
